{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/MinigameGifs.gif?t=1718157691\" /><br><br><strong>Please</strong> is a VR top-down rhythm RPG - while exploring the story, enjoy various rhythm minigames that are a homage to the large rhythm game genres!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/PleaseBorderLine_Short.png?t=1718157691\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/BossFightGifs.gif?t=1718157691\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>During bullet hell Boss Battles, protect your avatar by dodging attacks and using your physical hands to block them!<br></li><li>Play rhythm minigames that pay an homage to the genre, such as drum hitting, notes falling from the sky, blindly following orders from some random person, etc!<br></li><li>Solve puzzles that require controlling your avatar, using your hands, or both!<br></li><li>Explore the mysteries of this world, learn about various character's stories and how their Traumas affect them!</li></ul><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/PleaseBorderLine_ShortReverse.png?t=1718157691\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">World</h2>Traverse a mysterious world of in-between with a variety of residents. These residents seem to be stuck in this world due to their lingering attachment to their Trauma - get to know them, play minigames with them, and eventually defend yourself against their minds! Figure out what role you play in this world - and the mysteries behind it.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389290/extras/StoryGif.gif?t=1718157691\" /><br><br>The different art styles play into the story of the game; pixel art and low poly 